You have been hired to create a poster for a charity jazz concert held in a local campus's quad. The group playing is called "Smooth Digital" and is comprised of four alumni from the School of Music of the University of Illinois. The concert will take place at Main Quad of UIUC and on October 12th from 6:00 PM - 9:00 PM. Free cookies and beers will be served after the concert. Tickets are $10 per person. All proceeds will be donated to a cancer research. Intended audiences can buy the tickets at Illini Union at Room 208. 